Let's replace all loops using this iterator with

    for (HBasicBlock* block : MakeIterationRange(order.rbegin(), order.rend())) { ... }

or even define a helper function template ReverseRange() that takes a container by reference, static_assert()s that iterators are bidirectional and returns the range using std::reverse_iterator<>s created from end() and begin(), not relying on the presence of rbegin() and rend().

